    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing for a linear, 8,000-RPM power delivery. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-Variable differential, the drivetrain is mechanically synchronized to factory specifications. Extensive preventative maintenance has been completed, including a comprehensive rod bearing replacement and a full overhaul of the VANOS system. The chassis remains structurally pristine with proactive subframe reinforcement already performed. This is a zero-fault specimen with tight bushings, original suspension geometry, and a flawless exterior, representing the pinnacle of the E46's naturally aspirated performance legacy.",
